@NODE Break
  Status/break

    What I missed very often now with the AmigaDos Status command is to
    break a process by name! There's no somehow easy way to break multiple
    processes having the same name by status<>break!

        Example:

        I launched 2 multiviews and want to break them both (because arexx
        doesn't support shutdown any more). So I have just CtrlC to remote.
        For this I use:

            Status com=sys:utilities/multiview

        The answer is:

            2
            5

        Now I can break them by:

            break 2
            break 5

        To manage this to a script is a horror!
        What would be really easy to write and realize:

            break com=sys:utilities/multiview

        Thank you very much.


@ENDNODE
